} } const mapStateToProps = (state) => { let props = { statsLoaded: state.statsLoaded, uniqueUsers: 0, uniqueSessions: 0, requestCount:0, recognized: 0, notRecognized: 0, startDate: state.startDate, endDate: state.endDate }; if (state.statsLoaded) { props.uniqueUsers = getUniqueUsers(state.uniqueUsers, state.startDate, state.endDate) props.uniqueSessions = getDictCount(state.uniqueSessions, state.startDate, state.endDate) props.requestCount = getDictCount(state.requestCounts, state.startDate, state.endDate) let recCounts = getLayeredDictCount(state.recognized, state.startDate, state.endDate) props.recognized = recCounts.recognized ?? 0 props.notRecognized = recCounts.notRecognized ?? 0 let containedCounts = getLayeredDictCount(state.contained, state.startDate, state.endDate) props.contained = containedCounts.contained ?? 0 props.notContained = containedCounts.notContained ?? 0 } return props } export default connect(mapStateToProps)(OverviewPage)
